Blacknightmare::

Blacknightmare saw all figures that Orchestra was doing.  "You never 
had told me that you was a pilot" she said amazing While Orchestra 
was showing his skills.

When he said that if she needed a lift she answered smiling "YEAH!!!!"

She looked Orcestra smiling....
